title: daz3d - poser - DM's Enchanted Hill
description:
This package contains:

4 Scenes (.PZ3 & .DUF)

13 Props (.OBJ + .PP2 & .DUF)

- Mound with Hill & Rocks
- Tree Stump
- 2 Mushroom groups
- 3 single Mushrooms
- 2 Plants
- 2 Grass
- 1 Ivy plants
- Flute, parented to V4 & Genesis 2 V6

Poses (.PZ2 & .DUF)
- 10 Poses for V4, all with their mirrored versions
- Hand pose for V4
- 10 Poses for V6 (Genesis 2F), all with their mirrored versions
- Hand Poses for V6 (Genesis 2F)
(DSON Poser Companion Files included)

17 Materials (.MC6 & .DUF)
- 6 Blossom colors
- 2 Flute colors
- 4 variations for small Mushroom group
- 3 Mushrooms to mix and match
- Show/Hide Rocks

4 Scene Light settings (.LT2)
4 Camera settings (.CM2)

Expressions not included.
